OL,5, Fees for disposing of DIY waste at     
OL,6, council recycling centres in England   
OL,7, could be banned under government plans,
OL,8, in an attempt to tackle fly-tipping.   
OL,10,FAround a third of local authorities    
OL,11,Fcharge up to #10 an item for disposing 
OL,12,Fof paving slabs, plasterboard, bricks  
OL,13,Fand other materials.                   
OL,15,FMore than one million fly-tipping      
OL,16,Fincidents were recorded in 2021,       
OL,17,Fcosting local authorities almost #400m.
OL,19,FMinisters say they want to make it     
OL,20,Feasier for people to dispose of waste. 
